{
  "stem": "935.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then somebody took me, I know, and put me in a shower and lent me her clothes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I figured, I don't know where to hide from him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I really don't know where to hide from him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was, again, something like you say, you are a victim there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You don't have to do anything, you don't have to do anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And if he so choose it, he can do what he wants with you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were not physically, otherwise except for this creep, attacked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But you know, the closeness-- you suddenly sleep next to strangers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You breathe down at strangers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When you turn, they have to turn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There is no privacy anymore-- none.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Of course, I heard then the stories of the others who had come the same route I had come-- many, many, many.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "This Harry and John had brought about-- and Max-- about 150 over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was the last one, I'm happy to say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The same way I came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The whole way with Reina in the same barrack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then there was an occasion-- oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There-- there was a Jewish [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who was in-- going in between the commander and us, to see that they don't do too bad things to us, whatever.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He was an operatic tenor, who didn't, I hear-- he didn't have to be there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He volunteered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He was married to a non-Jewish women, lived in Brussels, and volunteered to see that things went all right.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "A very nice man.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The go-between us, let's say, and then the kommandant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he had told-- and there was one day when, suddenly, when I was walking in the courtyard, I heard a lot of screaming and yelling and pointing at the gate.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And the gate was open.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
